@node CLOUD "Amok"

@{b}Amok@{ub}

Color   = Red
Rarity  = SH(R)
Type    = Enchantment
Cost    = 1R
Artist  = Dermot Power

Text(SH): <1>, Discard a card at random: Put a +1/+1 counter on target
          creature.

Flavor Text: @{i}Crovax's rage was horrifying. Within moments only blood
             and shreds of flesh remained of the shapeshifter.
@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node CONTE "Convulsing Licid"

@{b}Convulsing Licid@{ub}

Color   = Red
Rarity  = SH(U)
Type    = Summon Licid (2/2)
Cost    = 2R
Artist  = Scott Kirschner

Text(SH): <RT>: Convulsing Licid loses this ability and becomes a creature
          enchantment that reads "Enchanted creature cannot block" instead
          of a creature. Move Convulsing Licid onto target creature. You
          may pay R to end this effect.


 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
