@{b}Craven Giant@{ub}

Color   = Red
Rarity  = SH(C)
Type    = Summon Giant (4/1)
Cost    = 2R
Artist  = Brian Snoddy

Text(SH): Craven Giant cannot block.

Flavor Text: @{i}What is high as a mountain and low as a snake? -Dal riddle@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node DREAP "Duct Crawler"

@{b}Duct Crawler{ub}

Color   = Red
Rarity  = SH(C)
Type    = Summon Insect (1/1)
Cost    = R
Artist  = Stephen Daniele

Text(SH): <1R>: Target creature cannot block Duct Crawler this turn.

Flavor Text: @{i}"The mountain's ducts will be like organ pipes, amplifying
